data.title: 以 3 到 5 分钟描写以下主题
data.content: Name one trait you have that you got from one of your parents. How has this similarity impacted your relationship? What do you think this similarity says about how your parents influence you?
data.answer: When it comes to a trait that I got from one of my parents, I suppose it would my father's trustworthiness. He is a person of his word. He would not talk much but when he does it carries unparallel weights. I love him and admire him so much that I want to become a person like him. Trustworthiness is the foundation element in any interpersonal relationship. Each time I am assigned a task, I will complete it within the given timeframe and to a high standard. As a result, I earned others' trust and forged healthy relationships. Regarding this similarity, among others, my father has influenced me positively, for which I am truly grateful. He has raised me to be a good person, a person who can be relied on by others. (133字)
